  "adms:versionNotes": {
    "@language": "en",
    "@value": "v0.4.0 — Oxford Kraemer Lab MV Hondius individual-level ANDV line list ingested (CC0, kraemer-lab/Hondius_hantavirus_h2026, Dr Moritz Kraemer / Oxford, Sam Scarpino, Andrew Rambaut / Edinburgh-Nextstrain); full Orthohantavirus NCBI RefSeq reference genome set (HantaNet, CDC Molecular Epidemiology, PMC10675615); research-linelist provenance type added; HealthDCAT-AP catalogue, schema.org Dataset JSON-LD, CITATION.cff (type: dataset), MeSH headings in API, .well-known/privacy-disclosure.json. v0.3.0: Ecological leading indicators (NOAA MEI.v2 ENSO, NASA MODIS NDVI); Berkeley Protocol CoC extension; cursor-based keyset pagination; ACH hypothesis scoring; THL Finland."
  },
